# SEO & AEO

## Every published app page

- `hero.structuredDataDescription` in `messages/en.json` — factual, includes Android package + iOS store ID when known
- `layout.tsx`: title `"{hero.title} — {hero.subtitle} | Zuki Apps"`, description from structuredDataDescription
- `buildCanonical` + `buildLanguageAlternates` on all indexable routes
- `SoftwareApplicationStructuredData` on main product page (`lib/appStructuredData.ts` Android ID)
- Rich pages: `FaqStructuredData` + `HowToStructuredData` (`components/FaqHowToStructuredData.tsx`)

## Machine-readable discovery

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `public/llms.txt` | Expanded per-app entry: support, faq.md, store URLs, features |
| `public/{slug}/faq.md` | Crawler Q&A stub |
| `app/api/site-facts/route.ts` | JSON catalog (`lib/siteCatalog.ts`) |
| `app/sitemap.ts` | All public routes |

## Rich product page sections (benchmark: hush-gallery, whistle-camera)

`screenshots`, `howToUse`, `faq.items`, `manual`, `tips`, `pageNav`, `useCases` (optional), `premium` (optional)

## Icons & OG

- `lib/appIcons.ts` — bump `?v=` when replacing PNGs (Next image cache)
- OG: app icon 512×512 or `opengraph-image.tsx` via `renderAppOgBanner`

## Home alignment

`home.{namespace}` carousel copy must match product page — stale copy hurts SEO and ad message match.

## Verify before ship

```bash
npm run build
```

Spot-check: store URLs 200, package IDs match Play Console / App Store Connect.
